{"id":"77be2bc87f57444e485e08517ecbb773268dd528927cfd1f9ebc543ab1a7085a","item_id":"a2c9fae429:0","text":"加载 RenderMan for Houdini plugin（插件）后，Houdini 中会添加 RenderMan Menu（RenderMan 菜单）。"}
{"id":"7271cb950c49bb3076dda1335f484c0ebfa2bff6028afa69837c0f32ebc0720e","item_id":"a2c9fae429:1","text":"IPR Render（IPR 渲染）："}
{"id":"d52ae25b23de98ef5d9e906966efc8dad42138f15db8f36b995cfbc295a502d5","item_id":"a2c9fae429:2","text":"Start（启动）一个来自所选 ROP node（ROP 节点）的 interactive render session（交互式渲染会话）"}
{"id":"9f4b8c0e3e60756e95db9a50a938c6c3949598c1453c3825834e4bac87c82560","item_id":"a2c9fae429:3","text":"Preview Render（预览渲染）："}
{"id":"34e156597e2a769d663d628ddcf456e1947253634bf0c693fe60e3d24bbf014c","item_id":"a2c9fae429:4","text":"触发一次 preview render（预览渲染）"}
{"id":"80ff4a75274b09d819e55fd722051be191453da8864edf54d08bbc8145f7c81e","item_id":"a2c9fae429:5","text":"Render in Background（后台渲染）："}
{"id":"ac04c2edf3b6b70acf7d69c9e8bbac4e61390b51044df16f6d1584e18c94202b","item_id":"a2c9fae429:6","text":"从所选 ROP node 开始在后台 batch rendering（批量渲染）到图像"}
{"id":"53e1e387e26f340316b7e291005f4d37afce3287561db9504f38188b4015d8fd","item_id":"a2c9fae429:7","text":"Bake Render（烘焙渲染）："}
{"id":"d3ae931db2d6a542c8bf1047adb633980026bf14a8e6bfdf229fad7bae3fac86","item_id":"a2c9fae429:8","text":"使用"}
{"id":"33632d53e1d0fd499e5af95936848f80babd328dea261c05ab05ee18baa5563e","item_id":"a2c9fae429:9","text":"PxrBake"}
{"id":"45978ecb2996bf78f07eed5be1b452a1dd2f2a93eda3aedb66f39ee36ccb2a79","item_id":"a2c9fae429:10","text":"nodes（节点）在后台执行 baking operation（烘焙操作）"}
{"id":"689e5e18755d5b21b43cec3c55c5c8511ebed9ba8ea2ae5962efcb9afab09de2","item_id":"a2c9fae429:11","text":"View Scene RIB（查看场景 RIB）："}
{"id":"9bdfbe3d1ba58c57e1aa778a631460ce6978ab672c2b2d551ff4d60258422a41","item_id":"a2c9fae429:12","text":"查看当前 scene（场景）的 RIB file（RIB 文件）"}
{"id":"ed7b7cb090eaba85433e51d6a0caf97d1c34101f4e45c18f2ee042ce3c2c1a75","item_id":"a2c9fae429:13","text":"Stop Render（停止渲染）："}
{"id":"2bce0f112deddc548b1e64cda74310c6dd9cb88e2d6fc7f7a93301a0b10edf6f","item_id":"a2c9fae429:14","text":"结束 render process（渲染进程）"}
{"id":"d7e83c7d29fe2268ad70774a60d1bed95faacd5af092d13a045d0133d4c75746","item_id":"a2c9fae429:15","text":"Flush Texture Cache（清空纹理缓存）："}
{"id":"ea388bb7c4919f266f3cab65ae997ef87c1da9bb6fb05c325b408ef8ddacd3ff","item_id":"a2c9fae429:16","text":"从 cache（缓存）中清空所有 textures（纹理）"}
{"id":"df6e0e08a1fd2dcdf7bb75bd60c5d0d7aeb0dc20121bc93bbe41ee6d663f71e1","item_id":"a2c9fae429:17","text":"Create Light（创建灯光）："}
{"id":"6d94adaccda3c2795dbc77df3e5d0d488e6955ee76340bbc47a645cf70a23417","item_id":"a2c9fae429:18","text":"快速创建 RenderMan light types（RenderMan 灯光类型）"}
{"id":"3063bae17428cd6179e257d086a2129f1a54b93860479b19a45f0785029991c1","item_id":"a2c9fae429:19","text":"Create Light Filter（创建灯光过滤器）："}
{"id":"b66c76b102441c555e8847fe7a7ac7d6df4b1b1ec587c9228577882e9ce88fd4","item_id":"a2c9fae429:20","text":"快速创建 RenderMan light filter types（RenderMan 灯光过滤器类型）"}
{"id":"66e009302ef039ec56b87b29cfee1a0f3dd41efe95fc318e6be7899fddf4566b","item_id":"a2c9fae429:21","text":"Create Material（创建材质）："}
{"id":"a84ab3a70c0eb47e1b50e4d6065a259d1976ac0f63d1f5511346aead0572297b","item_id":"a2c9fae429:22","text":"快速创建 RenderMan materials（RenderMan 材质）"}
{"id":"474b61b60dcacdeabb0ae358b55c8b39e0667be9d30b8c68b8e851d89654de39","item_id":"a2c9fae429:23","text":"Create Integrator（创建积分器）："}
{"id":"6d3588a368268a110897bbdc2f38651909bdc8e4b1dbad157fe12e6644740f93","item_id":"a2c9fae429:24","text":"从列表中为 ROP node 创建一个 integrator（积分器）"}
{"id":"8aa80778cc2e0cb1f0adc526e4f0b3f66cf745ea8306b316d73a3b8902ac474a","item_id":"a2c9fae429:25","text":"Create Display Filter（创建显示过滤器）："}
{"id":"cd4382c39526e9267c8c2d37d78eb00eff2e5e4ce1c812d9beac320ba4cf96bf","item_id":"a2c9fae429:26","text":"从列表中创建一个 Display Filter（显示过滤器）"}
{"id":"5ccb65ac427e5ef8358c11ba1d12ecfcd294bce8b88ef58da28b37767374b57e","item_id":"a2c9fae429:27","text":"Create Sample Filter（创建采样过滤器）："}
{"id":"39611a2700659800ef01b84a35569a8f96340be7c7cd2125ab43d6004e6ddab6","item_id":"a2c9fae429:28","text":"添加一个 Sample Filter（采样过滤器）"}
{"id":"6993df257652560d6a2fc4d6c517b5744f9b8038920b1bc60205ddee640de9dc","item_id":"a2c9fae429:29","text":"Subdivide（细分）："}
{"id":"c8b40055c9fa6973240e1eb8939062861afe4f24564caa3fee74efd7a682561e","item_id":"a2c9fae429:30","text":"为所选 objects（对象）添加并启用 subdivision properties（细分属性）"}
{"id":"d02cde97ca7646f73c3480ac9f508a7c16cdfbf09c3b0f6db537997cc1cd94e3","item_id":"a2c9fae429:31","text":"Stylize（风格化）："}
{"id":"7a383efb9c0d506215c7efb9661dcdd50a45d28addcb0357a040a421a1a16927","item_id":"a2c9fae429:32","text":"选择此选项会将 PxrStylizedControl node（节点）连接到所选 object(s)（对象）的 material（材质）"}
{"id":"448167051720c9cc8b89e85756a37c5614bf75c81835b58d6058074235d5b314","item_id":"a2c9fae429:33","text":"Aggregate Volume（聚合体积）"}
{"id":"d6083f5a9fdb67354f09efadaae30506a4f968144a2dbfe1de5672506061d5d7","item_id":"a2c9fae429:34","text":"：在 scene（场景）中创建 aggregate volume setup（聚合体积设置）"}
{"id":"b140745de50ff0b8ec03c35c3621df3d65c6d5089911933ac90a85086ad08c79","item_id":"a2c9fae429:35","text":"Holdout（遮挡）："}
{"id":"06fdc340eb38002280cf5f2dcf945a948e050a1d1ef31ebe0270e8c12d95df75","item_id":"a2c9fae429:36","text":"为所选 ROP node 设置 AOVs，以导出带 shadows（阴影）的 holdout pass（遮挡通道）"}
{"id":"178c4a9b8a4f5283fec54d8e2fbdd0f45dac2f59e05ec638508e237683b2042d","item_id":"a2c9fae429:37","text":"Open Image Tool（打开图像工具）："}
{"id":"f38a8f002508bcc34496311d16ff1394ee0c07d7ac577bc3beea8bf22d1dd3ac","item_id":"a2c9fae429:38","text":"打开 RenderMan Image Tool \"it\"，用于查看和 cataloging renders（编目渲染结果）"}
{"id":"db81d863b703634541fff696839dff15d1d8f75a9e3bbe3009b7017e41c1de60","item_id":"a2c9fae429:39","text":"Preferences（偏好设置）："}
{"id":"7979632a57674cc7ddc2c99a191159512f0d6e3c597addf81e577cd58a6ec402","item_id":"a2c9fae429:40","text":"打开 RfH preference window（RfH 偏好设置窗口）"}
{"id":"5528873c3e7c055c68a2b7a45823a31ecfa6058adbe2a7580df3331f5287cbcc","item_id":"a2c9fae429:41","text":"Update Lama Nodes（更新 Lama 节点）："}
{"id":"20415c02024ff03bc1e04bdd634f1bd41d96801b8832658c8d19d46e3f0d82fe","item_id":"a2c9fae429:42","text":"对于 RfH 版本早于 25 的 scenes（场景），如果使用早于 H19.5.501 的 Houdini 版本，需要手动运行一次顶部菜单 \"RenderMan\" > \"Update Lama Nodes\"（否则会自动执行）。你还需要手动更新 custom locked HDAs（自定义锁定 HDA）。"}
{"id":"5a587243983c852db3f398be41b5ac9755f91c00a4e03f2a921f020eb14fb80e","item_id":"a2c9fae429:43","text":"Help（帮助）："}
{"id":"7fbda70693348b984c14ee9f4e4ce34530013d886c8542c0a041c86d78b2c39e","item_id":"a2c9fae429:44","text":"RenderMan Help Documentation（RenderMan 帮助文档）"}
{"id":"b30a4ef12b03c83c583d281d8b511935e7560c13b806cad9c6a2bffaa7d7b7ae","item_id":"a2c9fae429:45","text":"About RenderMan（关于 RenderMan）："}
{"id":"54a65855ddb1e870a66e357c2a888d37c22406037130ab195c1efba293056f5c","item_id":"a2c9fae429:46","text":"RenderMan version information（版本信息）和 legal disclosures（法律声明）"}
{"id":"847cc618a0ab08ed39cb8592b8ff6b533a9b1784b47829a36dd97ca8a28d5ea7","item_id":"a2c9fae429:47","text":"如果自定义顶层菜单时移除了 Help Menu（帮助菜单）或 RenderMan - RIS tool（RenderMan - RIS 工具），RenderMan 菜单工具将无法正确安装。需要在 MainMenuCommon.xml 配置文件中编辑 <insertBefore> 和 <insertAfter> 选项，指定插入位置，才能让这些工具在自定义菜单中正确定位。"}
